{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Participants will be asked to stay in a fasted state for 12 hours before the blood test.",
    "The Geriatric Depression Scale 15-item (GDS-15) -Cantonese Version will be used to assess depression among participants.",
    "The validity and reliability of the GDS-15 were validated as satisfactory among Chinese older adults in previous studies and were regarded as a valuable method for measuring depression in older adults (Cronbach's α = 0.81-0.83) (53, 54).",
    "Participants will be asked 15 items referring to the past week, such as \"Are you satisfied with your life?\"",
    "and \"Have you dropped many of your activities and interests?. \""
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "The validity and reliability of the GDS-15 were validated as satisfactory among Chinese older adults in previous studies and were regarded as a valuable method for measuring depression in older adults (Cronbach's α = 0.81-0.83) (53, 54)."
  ]
}